Name: The Cup
About the game: The Cup is a fast-paced rouge-like dungeon crawler, where adventurers fight off hordes of enemies to find the ultimate prize: the Cup of Life. Use unique items and spells to boost your character's power. Find Lost tomes to learn powerful magic to fight off the hordes. You can also upgrade your character to boost abilities.
